  <summary date="2021-08-25T14:46:14Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Contact Lens Rule Modernization Act

This bill (1) requires prescribers of contact lenses to conspicuously post notice that the prescriber is required to provide a copy of the contact lens prescription to the patient, (2) prohibits prescribers from requiring patients to acknowledge a contact lens prescription release in writing or electronically, and (3) prohibits automated telephone calls to verify a prescription.</summary>
